'''Xenovet''', or '''XV''', was a [[Commenor/Legends|Commenorian]] [[Bioengineering/Legends|bioengineering]] corporation that primarily produced veterinary supplies for exotic species, especially those kept as pets by image-conscious [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Imperial]] officers. After the death of [[Galactic Emperor/Legends|Emperor]] [[Palpatine/Legends|Palpatine]], the company turned toward more philanthropic works, but soon after went out of business. It was located near [[Munto]].

